\newpage\EMPHASIZE{63. Constant Method and Self Reference}

\textsc{Objectives}
\begin{itemize}
\item Understand the \textit{this} pointer
\item Understand the uses of the \textit{this} pointer
\item Return a reference to an object
\item Return a reference to an instance variable
\item Understand the dangers of returning references to an instance variable
\item Make parameters constant to protect from accidental modification
